29:42.000 --> 30:07.000
The manager must, if in the case of an accident, excuse this tautology, very often there are situations when the manager cannot predict with a sufficient degree of confidence about the possibility, probability of the occurrence,

30:07.000 --> 30:25.000
then in the event of a contradiction, the direct task of the manager is to study possible places, situations where the implementation of the decision will be opposed.

30:25.000 --> 30:44.000
This can help him, including the correctly set goals of a specific study on the study of situations where and how this contradiction can manifest itself.

30:44.000 --> 31:13.000
As I said, if the manager does not have enough information to make a decision, then the only recommendation is that you need to spend time and certain resources to get additional information.

31:14.000 --> 31:33.000
In order to reduce the level of uncertainty, otherwise you will have to act on a guess, relying on experience and intuition. We do not diminish the importance of intuition, but we say that a rational decision should be justified.

31:33.000 --> 32:02.000
Since the decision is made in the condition of uncertainty, the concept of risk is associated with it. There is always a possibility to lose something, to part with something that flows out of the specifics of the activity of human society.

32:03.000 --> 32:12.000
And when making a decision, the manager must assess the risks.

32:33.000 --> 33:02.000
