42:32.000 --> 42:40.000
That is, there should not be any abstraction, each in its own way understandable.

42:41.000 --> 42:55.000
The second condition for the efficiency criteria says that the criteria must be determined with sufficient accuracy, without large costs and time loss.

42:55.000 --> 43:11.000
In addition, the efficiency criteria must meet the requirements of completeness, that is, reflect the significant aspects of the object or phenomenon studied.

43:11.000 --> 43:30.000
