01:23:25.000 --> 01:23:29.000
but it should not have been bought.

01:23:29.000 --> 01:23:32.000
This is the first mistake of the first order.

01:23:32.000 --> 01:23:41.000
The first situation in this case will mean that the lost profit could have been earned, but it did not.

01:23:41.000 --> 01:23:49.000
And the second situation, when the shares were bought, but it was not necessary to do this,

01:23:49.000 --> 01:23:54.000
is direct losses up to the broker's bankruptcy.

