When conducting a cause-and-effect analysis, it is always necessary to work methodically

01:24:37.000 --> 01:24:45.000
and study all the collected information very carefully.

01:24:45.000 --> 01:24:52.000
And based on the collected data, make a mental conclusion.

01:24:52.000 --> 01:25:00.000
Could the assumed cause actually lead to the observed effect?

01:25:03.000 --> 01:25:10.000
With all the apparent consistency of the cause and effect,

01:25:10.000 --> 01:25:15.000
