01:25:30.000 --> 01:25:35.000
You need to study every specific case.

01:25:36.000 --> 01:25:38.000
And one more point.

01:25:38.000 --> 01:25:43.000
It is necessary to keep in mind that if elimination,

01:25:43.000 --> 01:25:46.000
this is like a criterion,

