Probably, everyone is familiar with the fact that suddenly events are formed in such a way

01:29:15.000 --> 01:29:19.000
that one thing happens, another thing happens, a third thing happens,

01:29:19.000 --> 01:29:28.000
and their complexity causes the emergence of one or another problem.

